item.title: CVE-2022-4014|2024-08-03T01:27:54.169Z -- unspecified -- feehicms
item.description: A vulnerability, which was classified as problematic, has been found in FeehiCMS. Affected by this issue is some unknown functionality of the component Post My Comment Tab. The manipulation leads to cross-site request forgery. The attack may be launched remotely. The identifier of this vulnerability is VDB-213788.
